Check the Color of the Pencil.
Check the Type of the Pencil(Wood/Mechanical).
Check the Height of the Pencil.
Check how dark it is writing after writing something by a pencil.
Check the grip of Pencil.
Check the thickness of the LED.
Check whether you can write everywhere paper, wall,or cardboard .
Check by a pencil how many meters you can write.
Check how often the LED is broken and how many times you have to sharp the pencil.
Check how it is sharpening,whether breaking again and agian oe sharpened at one go.
Check after writing the text is readable or not.
Check whether you can erase properly or not.
Check is the shape of the pencil is as per the specification or not.
